name: remember the day when we are the one
description:
#6 - “all was in one, once, then divided ones brought the crisis” - An Embryoid, remembers the day when it is one with its twin.//

This is the universe of Altroverse 689. 

Dimension robots, known as Drakar, which is 3 species – Embryoids, Celluloids and Lumenoids. With their space vehicle Saga-689, they are seeking the Truth behind their creators, extincted Human beings.
